{"comments":"Metallic - metallic factor for PBR materials.\n\nRange: 0.0 to 1.0 (clamps)\n- **0.0**: Dielectric (non-metal: plastic, wood, fabric, skin)\n- **0.5**: Partial (oxidized metal, hybrid materials)\n- **1.0**: Pure metal (gold, steel, aluminum)\n\nControls whether a surface follows metal or dielectric BRDF in PBR shading.\nMetals have no diffuse reflection and colored specular (Fresnel F0 from albedo).\nDielectrics have diffuse+specular with achromatic reflections (F0 ≈ 0.04).\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Metallic"],"Metallic"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[40,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Metallic.purs","start":[40,1]},"title":"eqMetallic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Metallic"],"Metallic"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[41,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Metallic.purs","start":[41,1]},"title":"ordMetallic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Metallic"],"Metallic"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[44,29],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Metallic.purs","start":[43,1]},"title":"showMetallic"}],"comments":"Metallic factor for PBR (0.0 to 1.0)\n\n0 = dielectric (non-metal), 1 = pure metal. Affects Fresnel and energy conservation.\n","info":{"dataDeclType